<20_2 arg="5" /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />今天的点心我要吃全套的～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />～<delay frames="40" />
