	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太好了～<delay20 />既然弄明白了，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在就出发去钓<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><20_2 arg="5" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶？不对啊！<delay20 />
