	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />啊不是的，<delay20 />你别想太多了！<delay frames="40" />
<20_2 arg="7" /><20_2 arg="5" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />他一直很在意罢了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实我是无所谓的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也没有很在意啊～！<delay frames="40" />
