一看就很有<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的风格啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay20 />算了！<delay frames="40" />
