<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />我是大家的偶像，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" />哦～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～<delay20 />听着真的很棒！<delay frames="40" />
